  "body": "Attributed to @HenryNguyen5 \r\n\r\nProposal:\r\nChange Node to a singleton instance that keeps track of its own state.\r\n\r\nThis way, you won't have `getNodeLib` everywhere, and you won't need to store functions/class instance in your store.\r\n\r\nYour reducers/sagas would still exist, but purely for changing the node singleton state (in the saga) and keeping the UI synced (in the state with purely serializable data instead of objects with functions)",
